\section{Metodology}

\begin{frame}
\frametitle{Metodology}
The images had been downloaded through the ESA Copernicus Browser and the source is the satellite Sentinel-2 L1C
\end{frame}

\begin{frame}
\frametitle{Metodology}
The selection of the bands used is based on the best combination in order to highlight certain features of the landslide\\

\begin{itemize}
    \item True color: per evidenziare le dimensioni naturali del fenomeno visibili ad occhio nudo
    \item False color:
    \item NDVI:
    \item NDWI:
\end{itemize}


\end{frame}
